OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCompensation for Post      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FOffice victims to be sped  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fup                         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has announced new       
OL,6, measures to speed up compensation to   
OL,7, victims of the Post Office scandal.    
OL,9,FAn interim payment of #450,000 will be 
OL,10,Favailable to sub-postmasters who had   
OL,11,Fconvictions overturned, up from the    
OL,12,Fcurrent level of #163,000.             
OL,14,FLegislation to clear wrongly convicted 
OL,15,Fsub-postmasters is also expected to be 
OL,16,Fbrought forward next month.            
OL,18,FPost Office Minister Kevin Hollinrake  
OL,19,Fsaid the steps were "unprecedented, but
OL,20,Fthe right thing to do".                
